"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Yesterday I went to experience various cross-chain protocols，Such as Anyswap, Hop exchange, and xPollinate. I had a very bad experience. The speed is very slow, and the waiting time is very long. At the same time, the handling fee is very high. So! We must make some changes. I think we have another ways to solve these problems. In fact, we really don’t need to make an asset cross-chain to other chains. Unlike NFT, we only need to give the same tokens to cross-chain users on another chains. How to achieve it? Just let other token holders participate in our agreement, just like UNISWAP liquidity mining. In other words, CEX are the best cross-chain platform. The fee is low and the speed is fast. CEX can do this because there are a large number of users depositing tokens on the platform. In other words, every user is actually a liquidity provider. But the CEX did not provide liquidity rewards to these users. We can combine the two. \\n\\nThats great!!!\\n\\n[https://xpollinate.io/?fromChain=56&fromToken=0x8ac76a51cc950d9822d68b83fe1ad97b32cd580d&toChain=100&toToken=0xddafbb505ad214d7b80b1f830fccc89b60fb7a83](https://xpollinate.io/?fromChain=56&fromToken=0x8ac76a51cc950d9822d68b83fe1ad97b32cd580d&toChain=100&toToken=0xddafbb505ad214d7b80b1f830fccc89b60fb7a83)\\n\\n \",\"timestamp\":1638722078,\"title\":\"The second term，What are we going to do next.\"},\"digest\":\"3-2fU1H9AW73XlisracTe0SSUF5C9hk1P6cXBT3IPNc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x5D44965Db07306bD93Ea23B3E24f303D351ad7E2\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"YmbRKUbFVL75rswyL0drw6HEJ4MMIP_J8_hPLB20Qpc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"lFEGwPidkU-oKMItR76YOUdZnFVPD4Ta3SroJxso980\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"r1bxAZH5wsobCkOP1mrWl24N27ypq4JBzeE7PXzZW0KsPM86TdvJekug-wlUvJrOPZ2yHi1dILGT418pgw43gg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x176c4019f5408bfdbb404900a7680af4ee4a09ba8e8d359bd13f9f95899641cc1104db9d1d13770d2e775ba75